			"editorData": {
				"HowToTrigger": {
					"type": 23,
					"value": "- Load up GustavDev/BGO_Main_A\r\n- Use ReCon command \"oe SAM_Combat\"\r\n- Locate the zombie with the \"Possessed\" status (initially it will be Sister Shirra). Get them down below half health without killing them.\r\n- Before you end your turn, kill all the non-possessed zombies.\r\n- On the possessed zombie's turn, the monk's ghost will be unable to leave this zombie's body and play this AD."
				},
